tn.misc

Class LinkPropertyMap<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • tn.misc.LinkReadOnlyProperty<T>
      • tn.misc.LinkProperty<T>
        • tn.misc.LinkPropertyMap<T>
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    LinkDoublePropertyMap

    public class LinkPropertyMap<T>
extends LinkProperty<T>
    Description:

    This class is responsible for creating a map (hash map) for a specific link property. The map holds link IDs and the corresponding property values. It also has some map accessibility and cloning and modification functions.
